description: As a PP I want to track specific PP sessions so that I can attribute multiple commits to a session.

As a PP I want to track specific PP sessions so that I can attribute multiple commits to a session.

Acceptance Criteria:


guet session start should start a new pair programming session.


While executing git commit, the timestamp should be added automatically in the comments if the session has started.


guet session end should end the pair programming session.
